{The bidding has been as shown.   

This is almost the hand you held in Deal 4 - just 3 points stronger in \Ds. So you double, and again partner jumps to 2\S.  

That extra 3 points makes all the difference. With that singleton \H your hand is now worth at least 16 points. Add partner's 9, 10 or 11 and you are at game level. Bid 4\S.}

